27:The RebalanceOnUniswap contract is designed to maintain the VETH/WETH pool ratio at 1:1 rather than for profit. Gas costs are intentionally omitted to increase rebalancing frequency, accepting gas losses as a trade-off for improved price stability.
29:2. repayLoan function not used
30:The repayLoan function in the VirtualToken contract is currently not used. This function is designed to allow valid factories to repay loans by decreasing the debt of a user and 1. burning the corresponding amount of tokens.
